summary: Completed comprehensive Beauty Booking module implementation covering Admin, Vendor, and Customer web portals. All three web experiences are now fully functional with complete CRUD operations, dashboards, booking management, calendar systems, and all revenue models support. Created over 50 Blade views, 30+ controllers, complete routing infrastructure, and full business logic implementation. Remaining work: API enhancements (standardization, pagination, rate limiting), Flutter mobile app integration, comprehensive testing suite, and documentation.
